subject: Automobile Racing
Nascar Sprint Cup Series
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Jeff Gordon’s 84th career win, which ties him for third-most in Nascar history, put him in a comfortable position before the Chase for the Sprint Cup.
